Package civitas.celestis.util.group

Interface Group<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of element to contain in this group
All Known Subinterfaces:
DoubleVector<V>, FloatVector<V>, Grid<E>, IntVector<V,F>, LongVector<V,D>, Matrix<N,M>, Tuple<E,T>, Vector<N,V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayGrid, ArrayTuple, CircularQueue, Double2, Double3, Double4, DoubleMatrix, Float2, Float3, Float4, FloatMatrix, FloatQuaternion, Int2, Int3, Int4, IntMatrix, LinearColor, Long2, Long3, Long4, LongMatrix, Pair, Quad, Quaternion, Triple
public interface Group<E>
A group of elements.

While most groups are shallowly immutable, there are still mutable instances. For example, Grids are mutable by design since assigning every value in the constructor of a large grid would be impractical and hard to use.
